Hi Shea,

Thanks for writing to Dr Math.  In your first expression (without
factoring the 1 - 4(sinx)^2), change the (sinx)^2 into

  (sinx)^2 = 1 - (cosx)^2

and then simplify.  I see no reason to consider that answer better
than yours, so both should be considered equally valid.

